<h2><a href="/2752" id="entry2752" title="permalink to 'negative text-indent'">2752</a> &nbsp;</h2><div class="entry">
  <div id="etext2752">Negative(!) text-indent is in effect in the quicklinks list (over there on the left of the <a href="/">front page</a>). Handy... applying a style like <code>padding-left: 10px; text-indent: -10px;</code> to an element makes all lines of that element appear indented except the first one.</div>
  <div class="entryfooter">
    <div class="date">posted Tuesday, October 12, 2004</div>
    2 comments:    &nbsp;
  </div>
